original_title: Brooklyn: New Lots Avenue - Newport Street
text:
(1) New Lots Road, north side, between Newport Street and Church Ave., showing the Jacob Ryerson house. If standing in 1929, it would occupy lot No. 16 on the east side of Rockaway Parkway, between Newport Street and Church Ave. April 1926. Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.

(2) The same, another angle. April 1926. Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.

(3) The same, showing the interior of the barn. October 1925. Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.

(4) The same, showing the barns. Note the shingle cutter in front of the barn. October 1925. Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
